Standards-Version: 4.5.0

Package: meson-installer
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.7), ninja-build (>= 1.6)
Conflicts: meson
Description: install Meson using pip
 Meson is a build system designed to increase programmer productivity. 
 It does this by providing a fast, simple and easy to use interface for modern 
 software development tools and practices.
 .
 This package installs Meson via pip to enable access to more recent versions.
